---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<section class="section soluciones-section">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="badge reveal reveal-up">CENTRO DE AYUDA</span>
      <h2 class="reveal reveal-up stagger-1">Videos, descargas y soluciones paso a paso</h2>
      <p class="reveal reveal-up stagger-2">
        Accede a demostraciones, guías y recursos para instalar,
        solucionar errores y conectar tu equipo con soporte remoto.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="soluciones-grid">

      <div class="card glow-card solution-card featured reveal reveal-up stagger-3">
        <div class="featured-chip">⭐ DEMO DESTACADA</div>

        <div class="solution-icon viper">
          <Icon name="mdi:monitor-dashboard" />
        </div>

        <span class="solution-tag">Demo Online</span>
        <h3>Probar ViperPOS</h3>
        <p>Explora el sistema completo sin instalar nada. Acceso inmediato desde el navegador.</p>

        <a href="https://www.viperpos.net/login/" target="_blank" class="solution-btn">
          Acceder a la demo <Icon name="mdi:open-in-new"/>
        </a>

        <div class="solution-creds">
          Usuario: <b>demo</b><br/>
          Contraseña: <b>demo1234</b>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card glow-card solution-card reveal reveal-up stagger-4">
        <div class="solution-icon facturacion">
          <Icon name="mdi:cash-register" />
        </div>

        <span class="solution-tag">+34 videos</span>
        <h3>Sistema de Facturación</h3>
        <p>Capacitación completa del software, módulos y flujo de trabajo real.</p>

        <a href="https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1184xu1s4eirYN83QzL4Wfpsu_K3-Hqqs?usp=sharing" target="_blank" class="solution-btn">
          Ver tutoriales <Icon name="mdi:play-circle"/>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="card glow-card solution-card reveal reveal-up stagger-5">
        <div class="solution-icon autocad">
          <Icon name="mdi:server-network" />
        </div>

        <span class="solution-tag">Solución oficial</span>
        <h3>Servidor AutoCAD en Red</h3>
        <p>Guía paso a paso para corregir el error del servidor de licencias.</p>

        <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1jmlTTqccF4oUPupTYNCwNW_qZrrK8CwA/view?usp=sharing" target="_blank" class="solution-btn">
          Ver solución <Icon name="mdi:play-circle"/>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="card glow-card solution-card reveal reveal-up stagger-6">
        <div class="solution-icon soporte">
          <Icon name="mdi:headset" />
        </div>

        <span class="solution-tag">Soporte remoto</span>
        <h3>Conexión con AnyDesk</h3>
        <p>Aprende a instalar AnyDesk y recibir soporte inmediato.</p>

        <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/17cp_besLdN9NnNC1BpB9ox5oZVscdHLS/view?usp=sharing" target="_blank" class="solution-btn">
          Ver guía <Icon name="mdi:play-circle"/>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="card glow-card solution-card reveal reveal-up stagger-7">
        <div class="solution-icon demo-icon">
          <Icon name="mdi:laptop" />
        </div>

        <span class="solution-tag">Caso real</span>
        <h3>Demo del sistema</h3>
        <p>Mira el software funcionando con clientes reales.</p>

        <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1KjQ6-bD081vYcvX9h4eXr96nqyow17jM/view?usp=sharing" target="_blank" class="solution-btn">
          Ver demostración <Icon name="mdi:play-circle"/>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="card glow-card solution-card reveal reveal-up stagger-8">
        <div class="solution-icon descarga">
          <Icon name="mdi:cellphone-arrow-down" />
        </div>

        <span class="solution-tag">Android</span>
        <h3>Descargar FactuLite</h3>
        <p>Instala el demo en tu celular y prueba el sistema gratis.</p>

        <a href="https://factulite.net/downloads/factulite-v1.5.0.apk" target="_blank" class="solution-btn">
          Descargar demo <Icon name="mdi:download"/>
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.soluciones-section {
  background: var(--surface);
}

.soluciones-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: 24px;
}

.solution-card {
  position: relative;
  padding: 32px 28px;
  text-align: center;
  background: var(--surface-container);
}

.featured {
  border-color: rgba(245,158,11,0.3);
}

.featured-chip {
  position: absolute;
  top: 14px;
  right: 14px;
  padding: 4px 10px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  background: var(--primary);
  color: var(--on-primary);
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.3px;
}

.solution-icon {
  width: 64px;
  height: 64px;
  margin: 0 auto 16px;
  border-radius: 14px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 28px;
  color: #fff;
}

.facturacion { background: #00A8E8; }
.autocad { background: #10B981; }
.soporte { background: #9B5CFF; }
.demo-icon { background: #FF7A00; }
.descarga { background: #00BFA6; }
.viper { background: #FF4D6D; }

.solution-tag {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 2px 10px;
  border-radius: 6px;
  background: var(--surface-container-high);
  border: 1px solid var(--outline-variant);
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--primary);
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.solution-card h3 {
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.solution-card p {
  font-size: 13px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  color: var(--on-surface-variant);
}

.solution-btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
  padding: 10px 22px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  background: var(--primary);
  color: var(--on-primary);
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 500;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.1s, box-shadow 0.3s;
  font-family: var(--font-family);
}
.solution-btn:hover {
  background: #0891B2;
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(245,158,11,0.25);
}
.solution-btn svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; }

.solution-creds {
  margin-top: 14px;
  padding: 10px 14px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  background: var(--surface-container-high);
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--on-surface-variant);
  line-height: 1.6;
}
.solution-creds b { color: var(--on-surface); }
</style>
